review_text: A great place for a walk

Nice trial! The bridge has great views and I am glad it wasn’t destroyed and turned into a trail.  I really enjoy that Philadelphia has so many trials.  There are some many things to do besides being in city center.

Nice trail with a beautiful view of Manayunk and the city. It's so nice to come up here during the sunset and look at the scenery while going for a walk. It's also a good trail to run if you're into that

SO happy this is a pedestrian path and not a train line. Great spot to watch a sunset. Has so much more potential too! I would love to see it get made into some green space.. maybe add some benches too
